ddot.it/this ..content.. W3C RDF/XML syntax test: an XML predefined entity (ampersand) inside an rdf:about value. Single rdf:Description with rdf:about="http://example/q?abc=1&#38;def=2" carrying rdf:value "xxx"; the ampersand is encoded as the numeric character reference &#38;. Author: Dan Connolly.
